channel.description: ive spent 4 hours today just trying to change the name of a server, how do you do it???????? :confused: :confused: :confused: :confused: :confused: :confused: :mad: :mad:

item.dc:creator: @Nirvana.Marijuana Nirvana.Marijuana
item.description:
@Nirvana.Marijuana wrote:

[quote=“aviator, post:13, topic:70686”][quote author=mwiebelhaus link=topic=103868.msg1046731#msg1046731 date=1174788740]
yes ive done that but then when i go and turn the server on its like welocme to barrowscape we love barrowscape all barrowscape nothing changed?
[/quote]

Is a npc saying that? If so then you will have to go into your npc handler and change it to your server name.[/quote]

Dont post any more people im telling him how to change npcs too (On msn)
